 model. It’s equipped with features uncommon to many scooters, making it safer, more efficient and easier to use. Though it is not one of the cheapest mobility scooters on the market, features like the customizable captain’s chair and the above-average travel range make it a worthwhile buy.","You’ll be hard-pressed to find a model that offers as much as the Pilot 2310. The power scooter comes with several features that increase and maximize the rider’s comfort while also making this scooter extremely safe. Most noteworthy are the heavily padded captain’s chair with adjustable height and depth for even greater comfort and support, anti-tip wheels and a hand-operated brake for when stopping quickly is necessary. If you want to customize your experience further, you can easily remove the captain’s chair armrests.","The Pilot 2310 handicap scooter has a three-wheel design, facilitating its use for both indoor and outdoor settings. It comes equipped with headlight, horn, turn signals and rearview mirrors, all of which contribute toward its safety of operation. Most mobility scooters don’t come with rearview mirrors, making this feature unique to the Pilot model. So, whether you’re driving in a store or out on the streets, you’ll ride knowing that you can remain aware of your surroundings.","Picking the right scooter means finding one that offers sufficient range and speed for the amount of use you’re used to. If you’re a very active person, it’s important to find a model that allows you to get high mileage out of each battery. The average battery range among other scooters is 10 to 15 miles when fully charged. The Pilot 2310 goes farther than this average, offering an extremely efficient 22 miles per charge. It also travels at an above-average speed of six miles per hour, making it one of the fastest mobility scooters available.","The Pilot 2310 mobility scooter isn’t cheap on the market, but it offers a rare blend of agility, safety and comfort. Through numerous safety features, like rearview mirrors, in addition to a noteworthy battery range, you can retain your independence without sacrificing quality. If you travel a lot during the day, you won’t find many other models that provide the range and safety needed to get you around."]},"id":"649cef20-ca5a-42d2-92e0-7ce4aa919d58","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_59641","url":"/pilot-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"top-ten-reviews-staff","url":"/author/top-ten-reviews-staff","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Top Ten Reviews Staff","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"EcXXb3s8QKwvex3rQshgX5","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2014-06-04T13:32:14Z","datePublished":"2014-06-04T13:32:14Z","name":"Pilot 2310","synopsis":"If you’re willing to spend a little more money on a mobility scooter, you’ll be quite happy with the Pilot 2310 model. It’s equipped with features uncommon to many scooters, making it safer, more efficient and easier to use.","review":{"pros":[""],"cons":[""]},"strapline":"If you’re willing to spend a little more money on a mobility scooter, you’ll be quite happy with the Pilot 2310 model. It’s equipped with features uncommon to many scooters, making it safer, more efficient and easier to use.","language":"en","dateModified":"2014-06-04T13:32:14Z","id":"DJVvK6YqLoihiAues3RXhG","meta":{"title":"Pilot 2310 Review - Pros, Cons and Verdict","description":"The Pilot 2310 is one of the best long-range mobility scooters available due to its incredible battery life. Learn more here."},"products":[{"slug":"pilot-2310","url":"/product/pilot-2310","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T18:46:46Z","name":"Pilot 2310","dateModified":"2019-04-16T18:46:46Z","id":"oo6qQD3J7q6veBrhJadxiY","dateImported":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","site":"toptenreviews"}],"dateImported":"2019-04-16T18:46:46Z","type":"review","template":"review","social":{"twitter":{"image":{"status":"","height":0,"path":"/U